{"tid":1241251,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真普選，港獨 ，方舟計劃 與 自各移民，那將會是港人的未來？","createTime":"2019-06-18T15:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T02:51:29.000Z","uid":7736,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cb03e37fd9f38830c31eda06b8f735df8b36aaaf","tid":1241251,"uid":7736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:35:44.000Z","msg":"有鑒於香港的形勢不斷變，離香港變為大灣區，正在倒數緊，我哋要係時間到前，搵到一個香港人能夠生存的方案<br />\n<br />\n大家巴絲一齊分析下<br />\n<br />\n真普選 同 港獨 有咩分別？兩者間的利弊<br />\n兩者有什麼可行 或 不可行<br />\n<br />\n咩情況港人需要爭取真普選<br />\n咩情況港人需要爭取港獨<br />\n<br />\n中國體制下的 真普選，<br />\n有咩發生中共先會俾港人 真普選？<br />\n睇新疆和西藏，以中國的氣量真係會容許？<br />\n會唔會重蹈上一代香港人覆轍<br />\n真普選，最後會唔會成為 被中共用作，溫水煮蛙的伎倆？<br />\n大灣區的出現看似事在必行，大灣區同真普選香港可共存？<br />\n<br />\n（暫時我只睇到香港的存在價值，是支國<br />\n用來嚟，引誘同呃台灣的魚餌）<br />\n<br />\n港獨 代價，是港人承唔承受得起？<br />\n形成氣候足唔足夠，幾時先足夠？<br />\n香港地理上近海，近東亞的民主國家，<br />\n是比新疆與西藏更有優勢，<br />\n但他們真的會幫我地？<br />\n最重要港人真係有勇氣實行？<br />\n<br />\n兩個都係主權 重心問題！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">邊種真係做到港人想要的生活？</span><br />\n兩種結果發生之後，會有咩發展或蝴蝶效應？<br />\n<br />\n政治就係一門生意<br />\n以前日本戰國 真田家 由商人 變成 一門家族國家！<br />\n我覺得香港人，可以參考真田家的亂世生存之道！<br />\n<br />\n我地香港有咩<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好咩條件</span> 可以 同 中國 deal到真普選番來？<br />\n<br />\n或我地又可以俾到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咩條件</span>外國 幫港人爭取到港獨？<br />\n<br />\n可能兩個可能性，最後都冇出現<br />\n<br />\n第三種可能性，重返英聯邦，有冇依個機會？<br />\n<br />\n或最後變了港人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">方舟計劃</span>，<br />\n方舟計劃，現在計劃得來差不多，<br />\n或 聚散有時終須一別，各自各搵路移民？<br />\n<br />\n以上是小弟愚見，有好多盲點，請大家多多指點<br />\n大家講講"},{"pid":"ab716145396b659f9d2abcf9b515fbeefe99fbc1","tid":1241251,"uid":165515,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:38:46.000Z","msg":"中共唔會比香港分裂，香港沒有軍事力量。<br />\n所以方舟計畫比較可行"},{"pid":"8a8414a95e236bd6e0f5e75cf2a512720432220e","tid":1241251,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:39:45.000Z","msg":"我願意做民兵"},{"pid":"12ab91d63c70ec0dc1a72e4c7f523db70b4b1e48","tid":1241251,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a8414a95e236bd6e0f5e75cf2a512720432220e","tid":1241251,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:39:45.000Z","msg":"我願意做民兵"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:40:57.000Z","msg":"過嚟不過前提係軍備唔會無端端係天跌落黎"},{"pid":"b320e0fd6ecb5257cec95be5bc40d5c146fb2ba3","tid":1241251,"uid":7736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab716145396b659f9d2abcf9b515fbeefe99fbc1","tid":1241251,"uid":165515,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:38:46.000Z","msg":"中共唔會比香港分裂，香港沒有軍事力量。<br />\n所以方舟計畫比較可行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:51:09.000Z","msg":"睇蘋果港英解密，97前曾經有香港五首富，計劃夾錢幫港人買島，但最後冇實行到..."},{"pid":"3514a1cae2e8da698ae380e0486ac99d9da017b6","tid":1241251,"uid":7736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12ab91d63c70ec0dc1a72e4c7f523db70b4b1e48","tid":1241251,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a8414a95e236bd6e0f5e75cf2a512720432220e","tid":1241251,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:39:45.000Z","msg":"我願意做民兵"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:40:57.000Z","msg":"過嚟不過前提係軍備唔會無端端係天跌落黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:55:27.000Z","msg":"由零到有，都係要有個過程，<br />\n由計劃，籌備到實行<br />\n不過最緊要，有冇可能性？"},{"pid":"aef7b8bc1ed46fc7c498d7f1ca666d57604872c6","tid":1241251,"uid":7736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3514a1cae2e8da698ae380e0486ac99d9da017b6","tid":1241251,"uid":7736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12ab91d63c70ec0dc1a72e4c7f523db70b4b1e48","tid":1241251,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a8414a95e236bd6e0f5e75cf2a512720432220e","tid":1241251,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:39:45.000Z","msg":"我願意做民兵"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:40:57.000Z","msg":"過嚟不過前提係軍備唔會無端端係天跌落黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:55:27.000Z","msg":"由零到有，都係要有個過程，<br />\n由計劃，籌備到實行<br />\n不過最緊要，有冇可能性？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:59:41.000Z","msg":"咁就要睇我地 諗唔諗到，任何一個可能性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638f6406cc91248d0f1960551a175c8727603110","tid":1241251,"uid":165515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12ab91d63c70ec0dc1a72e4c7f523db70b4b1e48","tid":1241251,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a8414a95e236bd6e0f5e75cf2a512720432220e","tid":1241251,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:39:45.000Z","msg":"我願意做民兵"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:40:57.000Z","msg":"過嚟不過前提係軍備唔會無端端係天跌落黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:34:16.000Z","msg":"諗都唔好諗"},{"pid":"c32e190cab3cad42f5c09a194de9a522f015edc8","tid":1241251,"uid":10540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:14:18.000Z","msg":"仲有BNO平權做BC"},{"pid":"0cc80da508d96985e92a27359d3691b209d8e86c","tid":1241251,"uid":224323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:25:12.000Z","msg":"「普選」只係「港獨」嘅過程。<br />\n<br />\n有左一人一票選出執政者後，之後就要有經自己編輯嘅一部憲法。<br />\n<br />\n制憲完成，其實就係社會契約，民主受權，主權在民。<br />\n<br />\n好自然公投，實然獨立又好，自然獨又好。"},{"pid":"288af08e1e04834a128495240eab67f99e7d76d9","tid":1241251,"uid":224323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:45:11.000Z","msg":"現實問題係鑑於利益關係，冇人會絕對支持港獨。<br />\n<br />\n因為國際關係和地緣政治上，香港嘅價值就在於作為中國政權的特別身分。 <br />\n<br />\n大家揾嘅錢係因為呢個市場環境，而呢個市場環境就係受呢個身分塑造。<br />\n<br />\n所以，香港呢個位置，最適合做橋頭堡，或者跳板。 這是今日香港在國際關係和地緣政治上的處境。"},{"pid":"c8ac1b9bf805d1f57feec67b4967cccb502aa04b","tid":1241251,"uid":39575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:58:23.000Z","msg":"方舟計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JnVffhFDTA7KhDtjsfY58w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJnVffhFDTA7KhDtjsfY58w&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8ANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=57e92ac2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JnVffhFDTA7KhDtjsfY58w</a>"},{"pid":"bfc374764046654f85192f2d210266ddea11c918","tid":1241251,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T00:05:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7240045ac6b6f2030015b278e60f15994c310ec","tid":1241251,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T00:44:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0c947cc9d372c2e80c37ac12ed989cf0611e4aa","tid":1241251,"uid":270956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T00:59:00.000Z","msg":"其實講真，以依家情形嚟睇，真普選同方舟計畫係比較可行的方案。港獨呢個係終極大boss，真係幾乎無咩可能實現，大部份香港人依家都未有港獨的意志同決心。真普選應該大部份香港人支持，但其實都係一種溫水煮蛙嘅方式。長遠嚟睇，都係要打造方舟計畫。不過最大問題係資金，同埋香港人係咪真係願意拋低一切，重新開始。各自移民係最壞嘅打算，如果可以當然唔希望行到呢步。"},{"pid":"068ecec91db591bb098c915317a90bd5abf161fe","tid":1241251,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T01:56:49.000Z","msg":"人手置頂"},{"pid":"a2f19c2f3dbd7ef7f8b389e3544b20969dde7ac3","tid":1241251,"uid":36567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:19:45.000Z","msg":"支持方舟計劃 好過真普選<br />\n你地仲見唔到咩 根本社會上面嘅某某部門 同 某d人已經沒得救 比你爭取到真普選都改變唔到佢地奶共 到時都係執唔到政 <br />\n<br />\n建議方舟計劃要篩選"},{"pid":"26b0a70a28df67c4a88d23d87396019692e60f0e","tid":1241251,"uid":270956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:51:29.000Z","msg":"push push<br />\n一齊集思廣益，我地需要一個長遠嘅計畫"}]}